@startuml
title Blockchain and Block - Class Diagram

hide circle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Blockchain {
  -blocks: List<Block>
  +getBlocks(): List<Block>
  +addTransactions(txs: List<String>): void
  +validate(): ValidationResult
}

class Block {
  -index: int
  -timestamp: String
  -previousHash: String
  -transactions: List<String>
  -currentHash: String
  +computeCurrentHash(): String
  +hasValidTransactionData(): boolean
}

class ValidationResult {
  -valid: boolean
  -message: String
  +isValid(): boolean
  +getMessage(): String
}

class ValidateCommand {
  +execute(...): String
}

class BlockchainStorage {
  +load(): Blockchain
  +save(blockchain: Blockchain): void
}

ValidateCommand --> Blockchain : calls validate()
Blockchain "1" o-- "*" Block : contains
Blockchain --> ValidationResult : returns
BlockchainStorage --> Blockchain : load/save

note right of Blockchain
Single authority for:
- block append invariants
- full-chain validation
end note

note bottom of Block
Hash payload includes:
index + timestamp + previousHash + tx list
end note

@enduml
